308088976.Title: Whirlpool 7.4 cu. ft. 240 Volt Black Shadow Stackable Smart Electric Vented Dryer with Remote Start, ENERGY STAR
308088976.Description: Care never stops. That's why the Whirlpool smart front load dryer helps you stay in control and connected from anywhere. Pair this dryer with the Whirlpool app to start drying and track progress when you're away. (Appliance must be set to remote enable. Wi-Fi and App required. Features subject to change. For details and privacy info., visit whirlpool.com/connect.). Color: Black Shadow.

314379358.Title: LG Electronics 7.4 cu. ft. Ultra Large Black Steel Smart Electric Vented Dryer with Sensor Dry, TurboSteam & Wi-Fi Enabled
314379358.Description: Save time and look your best with a dryer that maximizes efficiency. With 7.4 cu. ft. of ultra large capacity and SmartThinQ technology, you can fit more in each load and control key features from your phone. So laundry day becomes your day. Plus, get ready faster with TurboSteam technology that removes wrinkles in a snap. Color: Black Steel.

312440282.Title: LG Electronics 7.4 cu. ft. White Ultra Large Capacity Electric Dryer with Sensor Dry, Turbo Steam
312440282.Description: Meet the intelligent dryer that helps you save time and enhances fabric care, all at the same time. TurboSteam technology reduces wrinkles and odors in up to 5 garments to refresh clothes in between washes. Built-in intelligence automatically selects the right drying motions, temperatures and more, and even talks to your washer to select a compatible cycle-making it the ultimate laundry hack. You'll even score high on the durability and style scale, thanks to the scratch-resistant tempered glass door and rose gold accents. Color: White.
